{
    "publish_date": "2012-02-15T14:31:50.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT12M6S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "STEVE: So I bet you think this\nis the part of the show where", 
            "dur": "1.73", 
            "start": "0.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to say, don&#39;t try\nthese experiments at home.", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "1.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;re right, except\nthere is one experiment", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "4.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we want you to try.", 
            "dur": "0.789", 
            "start": "7.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just look for the graphic\nthat&#39;s right here,", 
            "dur": "1.521", 
            "start": "8.119"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that says, try it.", 
            "dur": "1.16", 
            "start": "9.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s your signal that\nyou can try that", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "10.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "experiment at home.", 
            "dur": "1.01", 
            "start": "12.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everything else off limits.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "13.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look, I&#39;ve already given you\nhomework and the show hasn&#39;t", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "15.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even started.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "17.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, it&#39;s Monday and for\nme that means 9News.", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "21.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the local TV station\nthat I work for and many of", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "23.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you have maybe seen the segments\nover the years that", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "26.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;ve done with 9News.", 
            "dur": "1.07", 
            "start": "28.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I thought this would be a\nperfect opportunity to give", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "29.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you kind of a behind the scenes\nview of what it looks", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "31.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like as we prep for one\nof the segments.", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "33.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And actually what it looks like\nfrom beginning to end.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "35.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Today, microwave science.", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "38.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this is the best part of\ngetting ready for 9News is", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "41.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you get to go to the\nplayroom and actually kind of", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "44.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "work out some of the details.", 
            "dur": "1.05", 
            "start": "47.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the secret hallway that\nleads to the playroom.", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "48.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a place that\nnot even--", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "50.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, our employees don&#39;t\neven know about.", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "51.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s secret and this is the--", 
            "dur": "1.964", 
            "start": "53.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what the [BLEEP].", 
            "dur": "2.016", 
            "start": "55.604"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hey!", 
            "dur": "0.45", 
            "start": "57.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hey, get out of here!", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "58.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re shooting and--", 
            "dur": "0.885", 
            "start": "61.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CROWD GROANING]", 
            "dur": "0.84", 
            "start": "62.155"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Just get out of here.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "62.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Go on.", 
            "dur": "0.485", 
            "start": "65.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Get out of here.", 
            "dur": "1.57", 
            "start": "66.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER: Sorry, it fell\nout and I picked it up.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "67.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: How do you even know\nabout this place?", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "70.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER: I don&#39;t know.", 
            "dur": "0.54", 
            "start": "72.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I need to get back--", 
            "dur": "0.68", 
            "start": "72.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Make people get out.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "73.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, so the challenge\nis something fun", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "77.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to do in the microwave.", 
            "dur": "1.435", 
            "start": "79.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, there&#39;s easy things\nlike, for example, there&#39;s--", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "84.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we grab a soap.", 
            "dur": "0.78", 
            "start": "87.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if you take Ivory soap, for\nexample, and you put it in the", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "88.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microwave, as long as it&#39;s\nfresh Ivory soap--", 
            "dur": "4.13", 
            "start": "90.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I do it enough so there&#39;s stuff\non hand-- as long as", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "94.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s fresh Ivory soap.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "97.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ivory soap is the soap that\nfloats, and so we should be", 
            "dur": "2.575", 
            "start": "99.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "able to put that in the\nmicrowave and have it puff up", 
            "dur": "2.785", 
            "start": "102.135"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into these great clouds.", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "104.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a simple thing\nthat people can do,", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "106.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so we can try that.", 
            "dur": "0.98", 
            "start": "107.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s other things\nthat we can try.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "108.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you use a light bulb,\nfor example.", 
            "dur": "2.755", 
            "start": "110.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you take a regular light\nbulb and you put a regular", 
            "dur": "3.165", 
            "start": "113.585"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "light bulb in the microwave--", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "116.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "well, that would be bad because\nof the metal, but the", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "118.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "secret is you put it in\nthere with some water.", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "120.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the energy from the\nmicrowave actually heats up", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "123.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the tungsten and\nstarts to glow.", 
            "dur": "1.69", 
            "start": "126.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we can try that.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "128.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, I&#39;ve been saving these\nfor a long time, so that", 
            "dur": "4.88", 
            "start": "129.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you can see this.", 
            "dur": "2.645", 
            "start": "134.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here it is.", 
            "dur": "2.296", 
            "start": "137.465"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, I&#39;ve been saving these\nfor a long time.", 
            "dur": "1.788", 
            "start": "139.761"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at this.", 
            "dur": "0.901", 
            "start": "141.549"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Empty chip bags.", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "142.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So if you take an empty chip\nbag, made out of this foil", 
            "dur": "3.945", 
            "start": "144.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "kind of material, stick that\nin the microwave--", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "148.205"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll have to look at the notes\nagain-- but you stick that in", 
            "dur": "1.805", 
            "start": "150.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the microwave, it will heat it\nup enough that it will shrink", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "151.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you get a little miniature\nbag out of the deal.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "154.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So out of all these things\nthere should be something", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "156.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today, for the afternoon\nspot to be able to do.", 
            "dur": "3.97", 
            "start": "158.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Let&#39;s go find a microwave.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "162.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here&#39;s one of these cool things\nwith these chip bags.", 
            "dur": "3.546", 
            "start": "166.974"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Found this online.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "170.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So one of our researchers found\nit online of people", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "171.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "doing this so don&#39;t\ndo this at home.", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "174.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Find a friend&#39;s microwave\nand do it in", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "176.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "their microwave, right?", 
            "dur": "1.36", 
            "start": "178.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So find the plastic chip bags,\nand use the ones that have", 
            "dur": "3.08", 
            "start": "179.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what looks like little\nfoil that&#39;s inside.", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "182.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And again, if you have any\nconcern about ruining your", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "185.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microwave, then I guess\ndon&#39;t do this.", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "187.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this goes here like this.", 
            "dur": "4.03", 
            "start": "189.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This goes here.", 
            "dur": "0.91", 
            "start": "193.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, so now you don&#39;t\nwant to do this for a long", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "194.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "time, so we&#39;re just going to set\nit for like a minute, but", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "197.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re going to turn\nit off right away.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "200.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this goes in here\nlike this.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "201.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And let&#39;s do quick minute.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "203.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, we&#39;re ready.", 
            "dur": "0.556", 
            "start": "205.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we&#39;re going to turn\nit off once you see", 
            "dur": "2.044", 
            "start": "206.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the sparks come in.", 
            "dur": "1.386", 
            "start": "208.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So watch this.", 
            "dur": "0.406", 
            "start": "209.846"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s going to heat it up.", 
            "dur": "2.922", 
            "start": "210.252"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Bam.", 
            "dur": "0.962", 
            "start": "213.174"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s really cool.", 
            "dur": "1.044", 
            "start": "214.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Watch this.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "215.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Bam, look at that.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "216.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look what it does.", 
            "dur": "1.26", 
            "start": "218.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now you have to be very careful,\nbecause it&#39;s hot.", 
            "dur": "2.275", 
            "start": "219.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s some cool\nscience behind this.", 
            "dur": "1.815", 
            "start": "221.855"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the science of polymers,\nof course.", 
            "dur": "1.69", 
            "start": "223.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When these chip bags are made,\nthey&#39;re made out of long", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "225.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "chains of molecules.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "227.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So these polymers are stretched\nout, heated, and", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "229.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "then they&#39;re cooled quickly,\nso it retains this kind of", 
            "dur": "3.14", 
            "start": "233.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shape that you have here.", 
            "dur": "1.01", 
            "start": "236.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Once we heat it get back up\nagain, which I think you could", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "237.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "do the same thing with just an\nindustrial like heat gun, one", 
            "dur": "4.01", 
            "start": "239.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of those things, it would shrink\nit back down as well.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "243.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But here in the microwave,\nthat&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.05", 
            "start": "246.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exactly what&#39;s happening.", 
            "dur": "0.83", 
            "start": "247.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re hitting it with a lot\nof power, it releases it,", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "248.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and allows those molecules to\ngo back to their original", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "250.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "state, which is a relaxed state,\nand you&#39;ve got it.", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "253.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s kind of cool to see\nthe difference there.", 
            "dur": "2.809", 
            "start": "255.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just a matter now of\nwhether or not this passes the", 
            "dur": "2.281", 
            "start": "258.339"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "safety test with my producer.", 
            "dur": "2.09", 
            "start": "260.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She might say no to this, of\ntelling people at home to do", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "262.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this with chip bags.", 
            "dur": "1.94", 
            "start": "266.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think it&#39;s OK though.", 
            "dur": "0.99", 
            "start": "268.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s pretty cool went it&#39;s\nbeen online quite a bit.", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "269.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, here&#39;s one that I\nlearned a long, long time ago.", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "273.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to have a\nglass of water.", 
            "dur": "2.44", 
            "start": "276.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here&#39;s the glass of water.", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "278.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Got it?", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "279.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And to the glass of water we\nare going to put a regular", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "280.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "light bulb in the\nglass of water.", 
            "dur": "2.26", 
            "start": "285.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So here&#39;s the light bulb.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "287.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Got it?", 
            "dur": "0.71", 
            "start": "289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I know you&#39;re not supposed\nto put things that are metal", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "289.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the microwave, so to make\nit so we don&#39;t get that", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "292.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sparking, we&#39;re going to put\nthis down inside like this.", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "295.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now, you see how the light\nbulb is submerged", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "298.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there in the water?", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "301.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think that&#39;s exactly\nwhat we need.", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "302.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now, this whole thing goes\ninto the microwave.", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "304.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, so now watch the\nfilament insight.", 
            "dur": "1.985", 
            "start": "310.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when we start this, watch\nthe filament inside.", 
            "dur": "2.075", 
            "start": "312.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "See how it starts to glow?", 
            "dur": "2.595", 
            "start": "318.605"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s that awesome?", 
            "dur": "2.246", 
            "start": "321.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there it is.", 
            "dur": "0.874", 
            "start": "323.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here is our light bulb\nlike we had before.", 
            "dur": "4.21", 
            "start": "324.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the energy from the microwave\nexcites that", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "328.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "tungsten filament that we have\ninside, enough to be able to", 
            "dur": "3.63", 
            "start": "331.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "give off light.", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "334.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you do it for too long,\nthen it cracks and you&#39;ll", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "335.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "probably ruin your\nmicrowave anyway.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "338.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that&#39;s very, very cool to\nbe able to see what it looks", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "339.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like inside when you stick\nit in the microwave.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "342.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You just have to watch it\nreally, really carefully.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "344.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So cool.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "350.592"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, perfect.", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "354.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s two.", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "356.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is one of my favorites.", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "359.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It starts with a mistake that\nhappened years ago, as the", 
            "dur": "4.32", 
            "start": "361.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "legend goes, that Ivory soap\nis the soap that floats.", 
            "dur": "5.42", 
            "start": "365.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s the soap that floats\nbecause, supposedly, a long", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "371.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "time ago the person who was\nmanning the whipping device", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "374.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that made the soap in the\nfactory, left it during a", 
            "dur": "4.15", 
            "start": "377.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lunch break, and they came\nback and the volume was", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "381.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "overflowing and what they&#39;d\ndone is they&#39;d whipped air", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "384.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into the soap.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "387.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so what they found is when\nthey formed it into the bar--", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "388.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ivory is the soap-- here\nwatch this-- it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "391.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the soap that floats.", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "393.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So Ivory floats.", 
            "dur": "1.38", 
            "start": "395.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I guess that&#39;s a good thing.", 
            "dur": "1.795", 
            "start": "397.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you&#39;re taking a bath, I\nguess, it floats to the top.", 
            "dur": "3.185", 
            "start": "398.935"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It also is very, very\ninteresting.", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "402.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now, if we use those little air\npockets that are inside", 
            "dur": "3.25", 
            "start": "404.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "now, to be able to stick that\nin the microwave and watch", 
            "dur": "2.5", 
            "start": "407.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what happens to the\nexpanding air.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "409.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So watch this.", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "414.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What I like to do is\nto break it up into", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "418.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "smaller chunks like this.", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "419.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So break it up.", 
            "dur": "2.476", 
            "start": "421.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s pretty good.", 
            "dur": "1.344", 
            "start": "424.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It just gives it a little\nbit more surface area.", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "425.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK.", 
            "dur": "1.401", 
            "start": "430.509"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This will make everybody on this\nfloor very happy because", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "431.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you cook this, it has this\nbeautiful smell to it", 
            "dur": "4.57", 
            "start": "434.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that causes everybody\nto come out.", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "439.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here we go.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "441.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this goes inside.", 
            "dur": "1.028", 
            "start": "445.432"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You just kind of have to watch\nthe cool things that happen", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "446.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "inside as it&#39;s moving around.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "448.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ready?", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "450.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So watch this.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "451.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So take a look at what\nhappens inside.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "455.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As it starts to heat up, those\nlittle pockets of air--", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "457.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of course the molecules move\naway from each other--", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "460.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and it starts to expand and you", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "463.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "start to see some movement.", 
            "dur": "0.89", 
            "start": "464.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, yeah, take a look.", 
            "dur": "3.25", 
            "start": "465.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you just stick the whole bar\ninside, it&#39;ll work, but I", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "469.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "found that when you break into\nsmaller pieces you get much", 
            "dur": "2.27", 
            "start": "472.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "better clouds.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "474.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, that&#39;s great.", 
            "dur": "1.13", 
            "start": "477.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here, watch this.", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "479.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Nice.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "480.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at that.", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "483.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These small little pieces\nproduce these", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "484.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "great results here.", 
            "dur": "1.22", 
            "start": "486.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So look at the air that&#39;s\nfluffed into it and", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "488.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pops back out again.", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "491.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s hot at this point.", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "492.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to be careful,\nbut this is what", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "493.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it looks like here.", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "495.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is easy to do.", 
            "dur": "1.34", 
            "start": "497.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This will be perfect, and we can\ndo it in their microwave,", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "498.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and there shouldn&#39;t be any\nproblem with this at all.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "501.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now it&#39;s my job go sell the\nideas that work, minus the", 
            "dur": "2.985", 
            "start": "503.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "grapes, to my producer.", 
            "dur": "1.555", 
            "start": "506.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;ll let her know about the\nchips and the light bulb, and,", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "508.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of course, the soap.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "511.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I get the OK, and we write\nthe segment, and we&#39;re done.", 
            "dur": "2.978", 
            "start": "512.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "6.362", 
            "start": "515.728"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, it&#39;s not as exciting\nas all three of them,", 
            "dur": "5.972", 
            "start": "522.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but I can do it.", 
            "dur": "2.184", 
            "start": "528.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, the expanding soap\nis what we&#39;re going to do.", 
            "dur": "5.224", 
            "start": "530.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, see you this\nafternoon, bye.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "535.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, so here&#39;s\nhow it works.", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "539.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everything is set.", 
            "dur": "1.36", 
            "start": "543.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;re about 30 minutes to air.", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "544.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is live, so we don&#39;t\ndo live-to-tape.", 
            "dur": "3.69", 
            "start": "547.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Got everything that you\nneed, hopefully.", 
            "dur": "2.27", 
            "start": "551.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Sneak in the building, tell the\nproducer that you&#39;re here,", 
            "dur": "4.34", 
            "start": "553.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "set, and you&#39;re ready to go.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "557.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Today&#39;s different because I\njust have no idea where", 
            "dur": "1.765", 
            "start": "559.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they&#39;re shooting.", 
            "dur": "1.505", 
            "start": "561.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you&#39;ll notice that we have\nthis just in case the", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "563.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "microwave doesn&#39;t work, we can\nat least show what happens.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "564.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "TV tricks.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "567.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this is the control\nroom here at 9News,", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "572.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and Bob is the director.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "574.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And my producer is Jessica,\nright over there, and she&#39;s", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "576.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the one that told me that I have\nto do something different", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "579.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "today, so we can&#39;t\nbe in the studio.", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "581.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We have to be some\nother place.", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "582.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is normally where\nI bring guests and my", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "587.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "boys and those things.", 
            "dur": "0.99", 
            "start": "591.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If they do a good job, look,\nthey get to go to", 
            "dur": "1.672", 
            "start": "592.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "vending land over here.", 
            "dur": "1.638", 
            "start": "594.062"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this now is the set\nfor today&#39;s segment.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "595.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;m assuming that we&#39;re using\na microwave here and", 
            "dur": "3.66", 
            "start": "598.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we&#39;re just going to stay in here\nand do the spot this way.", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "601.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s definitely impromptu\nfrom what we normally do.", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "604.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think it will be fine.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "607.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: You&#39;re not\nmiked so this is us.", 
            "dur": "1.13", 
            "start": "609.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: No, so this is us.", 
            "dur": "1.72", 
            "start": "610.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ll use both hands, so I&#39;ll\ngrab this, and I, at the end,", 
            "dur": "3.77", 
            "start": "612.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "will hold this for you.", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "616.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The reveal is over there,\nif I ask you to grab it.", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "617.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: Oh, cool.", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "619.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right.", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "621.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Steve&#39;s very cool science\nexperiment today is another", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "623.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one of those in which he warns\nyou, do not do this at your", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "625.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "home, do this at a\nfriend&#39;s home.", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "628.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Because you&#39;re in\nthe kitchen, right?", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "631.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why do you want to mess\nup your microwave.", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "632.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: That&#39;s\nright, exactly.", 
            "dur": "0.7", 
            "start": "633.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: That&#39;s exactly right.", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "634.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do you smell that smell?", 
            "dur": "0.99", 
            "start": "635.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: I do.", 
            "dur": "0.22", 
            "start": "636.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: It&#39;s not eggs, it&#39;s\nnot, no, it&#39;s Ivory soap.", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "636.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: Oh, it&#39;s soap.", 
            "dur": "0.35", 
            "start": "639.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: So this is it.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "639.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you&#39;re going to\nneed Ivory soap.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "640.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: What a cool-- that\nwas a cool science experiment.", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "642.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Isn&#39;t it kind of fun?", 
            "dur": "0.57", 
            "start": "644.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Kind of fun.", 
            "dur": "0.49", 
            "start": "645.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: Once again,\nat a friend&#39;s", 
            "dur": "0.84", 
            "start": "645.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "house, not your house.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "646.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All right, Science Guy.", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "648.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "All this information available\nat stevespanglerscience.com on", 
            "dur": "2.595", 
            "start": "649.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the On-Air tab.", 
            "dur": "1.207", 
            "start": "652.345"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Got it.", 
            "dur": "0.432", 
            "start": "653.552"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: Look for\nSpangler Science.", 
            "dur": "1.296", 
            "start": "653.984"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, it&#39;s 4 o&#39;clock, and\n9News continues.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "655.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We&#39;ll be right back.", 
            "dur": "0.73", 
            "start": "656.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Just take that\nto Miss Kobrick, OK?", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "657.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "She&#39;ll love that for her little\nbath on Saturday.", 
            "dur": "3.13", 
            "start": "659.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "NEWSCASTER: That was cool.", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "662.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "STEVE: Three and a half minutes\nlater, I&#39;m done and", 
            "dur": "3.13", 
            "start": "664.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what do I do?", 
            "dur": "0.57", 
            "start": "667.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No, I don&#39;t go to the trailer,\nnot to the green room, fresh", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "667.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fruit and--", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "670.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m dusting the floor now\nbecause we&#39;ve spilled all over", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "671.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the place, and we&#39;ve got another\nshot back here in", 
            "dur": "3.96", 
            "start": "674.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about two and a half minutes.", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "678.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hard part about doing live TV is\nI never know what it really", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "681.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looks like until the very\nend and I grab the tape.", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "683.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you never know how it\nmixes down and what the camera", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "686.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shots look like.", 
            "dur": "0.695", 
            "start": "688.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And in this particular case,\nthere&#39;s just one shot there.", 
            "dur": "2.545", 
            "start": "689.295"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we&#39;ll see how the whole\nthing kind of played, but", 
            "dur": "4.01", 
            "start": "691.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s the only thing they&#39;ve\nallowed us to do is the soap", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "695.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in the microwave, because they\nwere fearful that kids would", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "698.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "try to put the light bulb\nin the microwave and", 
            "dur": "2.623", 
            "start": "701.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it would blow up.", 
            "dur": "0.587", 
            "start": "704.443"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the chips would be a\nproblem, so if you happen to", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "705.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "see that earlier in the show,\nyou didn&#39;t see it, if you know", 
            "dur": "2.747", 
            "start": "708.095"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what I mean.", 
            "dur": "1.548", 
            "start": "710.842"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Just the Ivory soap trick.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "712.39"
        }
    ], 
